Body:
Description: We were finally about to install the licenses you provided, but unfortunately, we encountered a - hopefully only - "small" problem. When we try to log in with the noted password (root), we can access the application, but we cannot comply with the mandatory password change. The password that was accepted at the login screen is now marked as incorrect, as shown.

Additional Information: Regarding the aforementioned server version and operating system, I am not sure.
